body:
Small android app (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.palacesoft.cngstation&hl=en) showing map locations of natural gas fuel stations in Sweden and Norway

Server module uses Gaelyk (http://gaelyk.appspot.com/) to keep track of station locations
name: Gasmacken
tagline: Android app showing location of natural gas fuel stations in several european countries
